data.description: This straight-through row home boasts an impressive array of features including a first-floor powder room and laundry room. The upgraded appliances and French doors leading to the deck are particularly noteworthy, adding both style and functionality to the home. The entrance room is a charming touch, providing a warm and welcoming space to greet guests. The partially finished basement is a versatile space that can be used in a variety of ways, from a home office or gym to a cozy den or entertainment room. This additional living space is a valuable feature that adds both convenience and value to the home. Overall, this straight-through row home is a well-maintained and updated property that offers a comfortable and convenient living space in a convenient location. Its many desirable features and amenities are sure to make it a popular choice for anyone looking for a stylish and functional home. One of the advantages of living in the Carroll Park section is its convenient location. It is close to several major roads and highways, making it easy to commute to other parts of the city. Additionally, the neighborhood is served by several public transportation options, including bus and trolley lines.
